OL,5, The number of parents having a baby    
OL,6, using a surrogate in England and Wales 
OL,7, has almost quadrupled in the last 10   
OL,8, years, new figures show.               
OL,10,FParental orders, which transfer legal  
OL,11,Fparentage from the surrogate, rose from
OL,12,F117 in 2011 to 413 in 2020.            
OL,14,FTwo-thirds of applicants are now       
OL,15,Fmixed-sex couples often in their 30s or
OL,16,F40s.                                   
OL,18,FThe report is by the University of Kent
OL,19,Fand My Surrogacy Journey, a non-profit 
OL,20,Forganisation which supports surrogates 
OL,21,Fand intended parents.                  
